f6xapW-mvtPMkPA=/750x762/72acf5fd-e697-40c2-9b96-7e996cfcdacd--Screenshot_2024-10-10_at_11.37.45_AM.png 2x\" alt=\"The Fits-anywhere waffle maker. \" width=\"964\" height=\"979\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/nk8W2lJH18sTCmWBUnxiH73p9DE=/375x381/72acf5fd-e697-40c2-9b96-7e996cfcdacd--Screenshot_2024-10-10_at_11.37.45_AM.png, https://images.food52.com/T30k2-fSerh3f6xapW-mvtPMkPA=/750x762/72acf5fd-e697-40c2-9b96-7e996cfcdacd--Screenshot_2024-10-10_at_11.37.45_AM.png 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n          \u003cspan\u003eThe Fits-anywhere waffle maker. \u003c/span\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Bella Kitchenware, Made By Gather\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eTo develop the line, Bella polled more than 5,000 people, many of whom, as the \u003ca href=\"https://bellakitchenware.com/blog/news/fits-anywhere-kitchenware-Press-Release\" target=\"_blank\"\u003epress release\u003c/a\u003e states, “expressed frustration with cluttered, bulky, black and stainless steel appliances that overtook their kitchen counters and cabinets.” While our team will forever love appliances optimized for performance (and you can peep some of them \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/shop/appliances\"\u003ehere\u003c/a\u003e), we’re curious if you—our community—shares a similar frustration with countertop clutter. If so, let us know in the comments.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n\n\n  \u003cdiv id=\"productCollectionRoot\"\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eFrom Our Shop\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n  \u003ca data-sku-id=\"43233\" data-vendor-id=\"903\" data-vendor-name=\"GreenPan\" data-category-name=\"Specialty Appliances\" data-in-stock=\"true\" data-price=\"250.0\" data-ga-grid-item=\"slide: 2\" data-product-id=\"11275\" data-product-name=\"GreenPan Elite Ceramic Nonstick 4-Square